      <title>任天堂分享关税恐惧，外国资金撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/nintendo-shares-plunge-as-outperforming-gaming-stocks-stall</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Mario Kart Maker Nintendo Co.的股票在七个月内跌幅最高，因为投资者放弃了日本优于唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税会推动美国股票价格上涨的视频游戏股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-07/nintendo-shares-plunge-as-outperforming-gaming-stocks-stall</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 07 Mar 2025 03:09:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
